<p>As we wrap up Game Day Phase 1, I am now putting out a request for help as we head towards Game Day Phase 2.</p>
<p><em>Wanted: Assistant Storytellers for Game Day Phase 2</em></p>
<p>Duties: Editing and Proofreading works in progress, giving feedback to other writers, coordinating with other Game Day leads re: overall storyline, herding cats, writing antagonist's actions. Must be willing and able to check in on the project on at least a daily basis.</p>
