														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-1283186">
									

<p>The structure for Game Day Part 2 is starting to form.</p>
<p>I need volunteers to coordinate storylines: basically, the way it works is that the coordinator for a particular storyline approves any stories involving that storyline to make sure it doesn't conflict with any established timelines. They also do quality control and such.</p>
<p>As a reminder: you need at least three SCPs or articles with ratings of +20 or better to coordinate. Anyone can contribute stories, but their work is subject to normal voting and review.</p>
<p>I also need suggestions for other storylines that people would like to write in (and pithy names for the ones we have). So far, I have three (353, 953, and 682) that I think have some promise. Keep in mind that one-offs are also possible: I'm referring to storylines that could sustain longer stories.</p>

							</div>

								
